HEADWORD: Enrockment
<hw>En*rock"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>en-</ets> + <ets>rock</ets>.]</ety> <def>A mass of large stones
thrown into water at random to form bases of piers, breakwaters,
etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

